@startuml
title FIG-03-02. Flawed Horizon Bank Payment Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F4F8FB
  BorderColor #2B4D66
  FontColor #111111
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF0F0
  BorderColor #9B2C2C
  FontColor #111111
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #555555
  FontColor #333333
}
skinparam linetype polyline

left to right direction

rectangle "Purpose unclear\nState: current or target?" as meta #FFF0F0

rectangle "Customer" as customer
rectangle "Mobile Banking\n(app/channel)" as mobile
rectangle "Payment Orchestration\n(system?)" as orchestration
rectangle "Approve Payment\n(business activity?)" as approve
rectangle "Fraud Screening" as fraud
rectangle "Sanctions" as sanctions
rectangle "Core Banking" as core
rectangle "Payment Rail\nexternal?" as rail
rectangle "Operations\nowner?" as ops

meta -[hidden]down-> mobile
customer -right-> mobile : uses
mobile -right-> orchestration
orchestration -right-> approve : updates
approve -right-> core
orchestration -down-> fraud : check
fraud -right-> sanctions
orchestration -right-> rail : sends
rail -right-> core : updates
ops -up-> orchestration

note bottom of rail
Unexplained external rail.
No visible trust boundary.
end note

note bottom of core
No exception, rejection or
repair path is shown.
end note

note bottom of approve
Mixed business activity and
software/system concepts.
end note

@enduml
